                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Conger</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-01-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 10, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay states that our suggestion regarding negotiations, indemnity, and
                    commercial treaties, being opposed by Germany and Japan, will not be pressed. We
                    are asking that representatives of other powers be instructed by their
                    Governments to exert utmost efforts to conclude negotiations in Peking.)</p>
            </div>
